, T., Chen, J., A North Pacific decadal variability in subduction rate (2009) Geophys. Res. Lett, 36, pp. L22602. , doi:10.1029/ 2009GL040914; Qu, T., Xie, S.-P., Mitsudera, H., Ishida, A., Subduction of the North Pacific mode waters in a global eddy-resolving GCM (2002) J. Phys. Oceanogr., 32, pp. 746-763; Sasaki, H., Xie, S.-P., Taguchi, B., Nonaka, M., Masumoto, Y., Seasonal variations of the Hawaiian Lee Countercurrent induced by the meridional migration of the trade winds (2010) Ocean Dyn., 60, pp. 705-715; Sasaki, Y.N., Schneider, N., Maximenko, N., Lebedev, K., Observational evidence for propagation of decadal spiciness anomalies in the North Pacific (2010) Geophys. Res. Lett., 37, pp. L07708. , doi:10.1029/2010GL042716; Schneider, N., Miller, A.J., Predicting western North Pacific Ocean climate (2001) J. Climate, 14, pp. 3997-4002; Schneider, N., Miller, A.J., Alexander, M.A., Deser, C., Subduction of decadal North Pacific temperature anomalies: Observations and dynamics (1999) J. Phys. Oceanogr., 29, pp. 1056-1070; Suga, T., Hanawa, K., Toba, Y., Subtropical mode water in the 1378E section (1989) J. Phys. Oceanogr., 19, pp. 1605-1618; Suga, T., Takei, Y., Hanawa, K., Thermostad distribution in the North Pacific subtropical gyre: The central mode water and the subtropical mode water (1997) J. Phys. Oceanogr., 27, pp. 140-152; Sugimoto, S., Hanawa, K., Remote reemergence areas of winter sea surface temperature anomalies in the North Pacific (2005) Geophys. Res. Lett., 32, pp. L01606. , doi:10.1029/2004GL021410; Taguchi, B., Xie, S.-P., Schneider, N., Nonaka, M., Sasaki, H., Sasai, Y., Decadal variability of the Kuroshio Extension: Observations and an eddy-resolving model hindcast (2007) J. Climate, 20, pp. 2357-2377; Thompson, L., Dawe, J.T., Propagation of wind and buoyancy forced density anomalies in the North Pacific: Dependence on ocean model resolution (2007) OceanModell., 16, pp. 277-284; Tokinaga, H., Xie, S.-P., Kobashi, F., Tanimoto, Y., (2009) Local